  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\nImplement network based token filtering and balance calculation in the wallet home.\r\n\r\n### Depends on #18417\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n- By default, all three networks are selected\r\n- The balances per chain/network are displayed next to the checkbox\r\n- When there is any change in the network, the tokens and aggregated fiat balance should be re-calculated depending on the selected network and displayed in the Wallet home\r\n- When the user moves away from the Wallet tab, the network selection will reset to default\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- Balances per chain/network are displayed next to the checkbox\r\n- Tokens and aggregated fiat balances reflect the selected networks\r\n- The networks should reset to default when the user moves away from the Wallet tab\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\n- Re-use the existing sub `:wallet/aggregated-tokens-and-balance`\r\n",
